title: When will the official Phunky Fungi Launch take Place?
description: The official Phunky Fungi launch is still to be announced. Expect to see the fungi taking over the metaverse by the first half of March 2022. Further updates will be revealed exclusively in our Discord Server.

title: How Can I Join You?
description: We have over 30k discord members grinding it out in the Phunky Casino for a chance to be Whitelisted. We still have some whitelist spots left but they are filling up quickly. Be sure to join our discord server by using the following link: Phunky Fungi (discord.com)

title: How many Phunky Fungi are taking over the Phunky Forest?
description: There will be 9200 phunky phuckers taking over the phunky forest starting in March 2022. We look forward to having you join in on the action!

title: Will Phunky Fungi have Utility?
description: Hell yes they will! Head over to the road map section over website to see what we have in spore.

title: What Blockchain is the Project Hosted On?
description: Phunky Fungi will be created on the Ethereum Blockchain

title: When can I see my NFT?
description: Your Phunky Fungi NFT will be revealed several days after we have minted out. Stay tuned in our discord for further information.
